sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Tenant A User
    participant API as API
    participant Cache
    participant DB

    rect rgb(255,245,245)
    Note over A,DB: Before mitigation
    A->>API: GET /invoice/42
    API->>Cache: GET invoice:42
    Cache-->>API: Tenant B record
    API-->>A: Cross-tenant leak
    end

    rect rgb(245,255,245)
    Note over A,DB: After mitigation
    A->>API: GET /invoice/42
    API->>Cache: GET tenant:a:invoice:42
    Cache-->>API: miss
    API->>DB: SELECT ... WHERE tenant_id='tenant-a' AND id=42
    DB-->>API: Tenant A record only
    API-->>A: Scoped response
    end
